Make sure that all the test scripts in this directory and in all the 
subdirectories (*.sh) has executable flag.

Edit setup.sh for global settings. 

For the particular tests, you can override some of the global settings. 
Edit the particular test scripts in the "tests" subdirectory. Each file has
a section marked between "Edit this" and "Do not edit after this". Here, you can
override the global settings. 

Ensure that you have valid credentials to use the external resources.
